'''Krischka Stoffels''', ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Namibiya]] . Krischka yakoze firime nyinshi zizwi cyane harimo ''Gesie muri die glas'' na ''Tjiraa'' .  Usibye icyerekezo, ni na producer, umwanditsi, cinematografi akaba n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
She was born in Windhoek, Namibia.

== Career ==
Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakoze filimi ngufi, ''Gesie muri die glas'', yatsindiye igihembo kidasanzwe cyo kuvuga muri [[Namibiya|Namibian]] Film and Theatre Awards.  ''Nitsinzi'', yakoze Tjiraa ye filimi ya kabiri ngufi. Iyi filime ikurikira Vezuva, umukobwa ukiri muto wa Ovaherero wagarutse avuye kwiga mu mahanga, mu [[Budage]], gusa yaje kubona ko mubyara we washatse yitabye Imana, kandi ko nk'uko bisanzwe, biteganijwe ko azashyingira umupfakazi wa mubyara we.  Iyi filime yatewe inkunga na komisiyo ishinzwe amafilime ya [[Namibiya]] kandi yatoranijwe kugira ngo yerekanwe mu birori mpuzamahanga  bya filime, harimo iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime rya Afurika Diaspora . 

